name: The God of Pizza Thunder
description:
Meet our god!!
Zeus is not only using thunder as his power to fight his enemy, but he makes pizza from thunder too!!
Pizzeus is managed by us, supported and funded by Zeus as the founder to provide his homemade pizza to all humans on earth. Here is the first moment when he makes Pizza "Howly Pizzeus" with his power, and sends it to earth.

Pizza: Howly Pizzeus
